Text: LPL Financial LLC grew its stake in Vanguard High Dividend Yield ETF by 9.7% in the 2nd quarter. LPL Financial LLC now owns 2,884,600 shares of the company's stock worth $252,056,000 after buying an additional 255,244 shares in the last quarter.
